CH3OH_NOAAPTR_ppbv,  ppbv, Gas_CH3OH_InSitu_S_AVMR, (CH3OH) methanol
CH3CN_NOAAPTR_ppbv,  ppbv, Gas_CH3CN_InSitu_S_AVMR, (CH3CN) acetonitrile
CH3CHO_NOAAPTR_ppbv,  ppbv, Cas_CH3CHO_InSitu_S_AVMR, (CH3CHO) acetaldehyde. Interferences from ethanol and ethylene glycol have been subtracted (using NOAA LTOF data for ethylene glycol)
C2H5OH_NOAAPTR_ppbv,  ppbv, Gas_C2H5OH_InSitu_S_AVMR, (C2H5OH) ethanol
CH3SH_NOAAPTR_ppbv,  ppbv, Gas_CH3SH_InSitu_S_AVMR, (CH3SH) methanethiol, using calibration factor for DMS
Acrolein_NOAAPTR_ppbv,  ppbv, Gas_Acrolein_InSitu_S_AVMR, (C3H4O) acrolein
AcetonePropanal_NOAAPTR_ppbv,  ppbv, Gas_AcetoneAndPropanal_InSitu_S_AVMR, (C3H6O) sum of acetone (dominant isomer) and propanal, using calibration factor for acetone
DMS_NOAAPTR_ppbv,  ppbv, Gas_DMS_InSitu_S_AVMR, (C2H6S) dimethyl sulfide with possible small contributions from ethanethiol
C5H8_NOAAPTR_ppbv,  ppbv, Gas_Isoprene_InSitu_S_AVMR, (C5H8) isoprene and possible fragments from cycloalkanes and aldehydes. Interferences have been subtracted following methods described by Coggon et al (2023)
MVKMAC_NOAAPTR_ppbv,  ppbv, Gas_MVKAndMAC_InSitu_S_AVMR, (C4H6O) sum of methyl vinyl ketone, methacrolein, and small amounts of crotonaldehyde, using weighted calibration factor for MVK (0.637) and MACR (0.363)
Benzene_NOAAPTR_ppbv,  ppbv, Gas_Benzene_InSitu_S_AVMR, (C6H6) benzene
Toluene_NOAAPTR_ppbv,  ppbv, Gas_Toluene_InSitu_S_AVMR, (C7H8) toluene with possible small contributions of fragments from ethyltoluene
Styrene_NOAAPTR_ppbv,  ppbv, Gas_Styrene_InSitu_S_AVMR, (C8H8) styrene
Benzaldehyde_NOAAPTR_ppbv,  ppbv, Gas_Benzaldehyde_InSitu_S_AVMR, (C7H6O) benzaldehyde
C8Aromatics_NOAAPTR_ppbv,  ppbv, Gas_C8Aromatics_InSitu_M_AVMR, (C8H10) sum of m-xylene, p-xylene, o-xylene, and ethyl benzene
C9Aromatics_NOAAPTR_ppbv,  ppbv, Gas_C9Aromatics_InSitu_M_AVMR, (C9H12) sum of C9 aromatics
Naphthalene_NOAAPTR_ppbv,  ppbv, Gas_Naphthalene_InSitu_S_AVMR, (C10H8) naphthalene
Octanal_NOAAPTR_ppbv,  ppbv, Gas_Octanal_InSitu_S_AVMR, (C8H16O) octanal and small amounts of octanone
Monoterpenes_NOAAPTR_ppbv,  ppbv, Gas_Monoterpenes_InSitu_M_AVMR, (C10H16) sum of monoterpenes and possible contributions from fragments of oxygenated monoterpenoids such as eucalyptol.
Nonanal_NOAAPTR_ppbv,  ppbv, Gas_Nonanal_InSitu_M_AVMR, (C9H18O) nonanal and small amounts of nonanone
C7H4ClF3_NOAAPTR_ppbv,  ppbv, Gas_C7H4ClF3_InSitu_S_AVMR, (C7H4ClF3) parachlorobenzotrifluoride
C10H30O5Si5_NOAAPTR_ppbv,  ppbv, Gas_C10H30O5Si5_InSitu_S_AVMR, (C10H30O5Si5) decamethylcyclopentasiloxane
